<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Reset Your UniNav Password</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #4f46e5;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      padding: 25px;
      border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-top: none;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    .button {
      display: block;
      background-color: #4f46e5;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-align: center;
      width: 200px;
    }
    .expiry {
      color: #ef4444;
      font-size: 14px;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Reset Your Password</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <p>Hi <%= firstName %> <%= lastName %>,</p>
    
    <p>We received a request to reset your password for your UniNav account. To proceed with the password reset, click the button below:</p>
    
    <a href="<%= resetUrl %>" class="button">Reset Password</a>
    
    <p class="expiry">This password reset link will expire in 1 hour.</p>
    
    <p>If you didn't request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email. Your password will remain unchanged.</p>
    
    <p>For your security, please:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Never share your password with anyone</li>
      <li>Create a strong password with a mix of letters, numbers, and symbols</li>
      <li>Use a unique password for your UniNav account</li>
    </ul>
    
    <p>Best regards,<br>The UniNav Team</p>
  </div>
  <div class="footer">
    <p>Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> UniNav. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p>This email was sent to reset your password. If you have any questions, please contact our support team at support@uninav.com</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>